  "keyFeatures": [
    "Rich context display with registers, stack, disassembly and backtrace on every stop",
    "glibc, jemalloc, musl (mallocng) heap inspection and visualization",
    "Capstone + Unicorn powered disassembly and emulation with resolved operands",
    "Decompiler integration with IDA Pro, Binary Ninja, Ghidra, and angr",
    "Linux kernel debugging (SLUB, buddy allocator, BPF, netfilter, tasks)",
    "ROP gadget finding via ROPgadget and ropper",
    "Memory search, telescoping, leak finding, and ASLR manipulation",
    "WinDbg compatibility command layer",
    "Support for both GDB and LLDB (experimental)",
    "Cross-architecture support including ARM, RISC-V, MIPS, and more"
  ],
